Operations:
	- add/2
		Arguments:
			index - start insertion position
			string - string to insert
	- del/2
		Arguments:
			index - start deletion position
			lenght - number of characters to delete
	- rep/3
		Arguments:
			index - start replacement position
			lenght - number of characters to delete
			string - string to insert after replacement position
			
			
The messages are sent using JSON.
Example operation - add(2,asdasd) on state 11,2 :

---
{
    "msg": [
        {
            "operation": [
                {
                    "_type": "add",
                    "_args": [
                        1,
                        "asdf"
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "_type": "add",
                    "_args": [
                        1,
                        "asdf"
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "state": [
                11,
                2
            ]
        }
    ]
}
    "operation":{
        "type":"add",
        "arg":[
            2,
            "asdasd"
        ]
    }
}
---
